Ing '''Basil''' (''Ocimum basilicum'') ({{pron-en|ˈbæzəl}} o {{IPA|/ˈbeɪzəl/}}), ning [[Family (biology)|Familiang]] [[Lamiaceae]] (mints), metung yang mabayang mababang-daragul a [[herb]].
Ing Basil magagamit ya kareng pamaglutu kareng [[Italian cuisine]], ampo kareng [[Southeast Asia]]n cuisine ning [[Cuisine of Thailand|Thailand]], [[Cuisine of Vietnam|Vietnam]], [[Cuisine of Cambodia|Cambodia]], ampong [[Cuisine of Laos|Laos]]. Ing tanaman balamu lalasa yang [[anise]], a atin masikan, mapakla, mayumung bau.  

